Hi friends, Here I have created a program of Encrypting text using Ceaser cipher in JAVA. I have used very simple and straightforward approach. My program include methods 
like Encryption, Decryption and Enchanced Encryption(i.e. Encryption using two keys). I hope you will enjoy it. Happy Coding :)

*********Output*********

Enter your string:
My favourite animal is Dog.
*****Menu*****
1. Encryption
2. Decryption
3. Enhanced Encryption
Enter your choice: 
1
Enter the key:
9361
Your Encrypted Text is:
Nz gbwpvsjuf bojnbm jt Eph.
